:"focal-point","product_2":""}},"1642551013e82b51bf-4":{"type":"image","settings":{"link":"","title":"Enjoy the journey","text":"<p>New embroidered triblend crewnecks.<\/p><p><br\/>Life is made up of small moments and valuable experiences. Don't miss them on the way to the goal.<\/p>","enable_overlay":true,"enable_popup":true,"product_1":"enjoy-the-journey","product_2":""}},"1642551013e82b51bf-5":{"type":"image","settings":{"link":"","title":"","text":"<p>New embroidered crewneck pullover sweatshirts coming soon!<\/p>","enable_overlay":true,"enable_popup":true,"product_1":"leather-patch-hoodie","product_2":""}},"7de6a3d4-02b2-4560-9610-e839d013ccdf":{"type":"image","disabled":true,"settings":{"link":"","title":"Leather Patch","text":"<p>Super soft zip-up hoody features a custom-sewn leather patch ampersand along with leather trim details on the drawstring. The natural vegetable-tanned leather will darken with age and wear. <\/p>","enable_overlay":true,"enable_popup":true,"product_1":"leather-patch-hoodie","product_2":""}},"2e123d2f-4c94-4fff-a23a-9213b3c9064f":{"type":"image","disabled":true,"settings":{"link":"","title":"","text":"<p>Dieter Rams 10 Principles of Good Design.<\/p><p><\/p><p>Letterpress print from when I backed @gary_hustwit Kickstarter for the upcoming Dieter Rams documentary.<\/p>","enable_overlay":true,"enable_popup":false,"product_1":"","product_2":""}},"aa3e38c7-4252-4cc7-b4d5-623162b3abae":{"type":"image","disabled":true,"settings":{"link":"","title":"","text":"<p>Our \"And Then I Woke Up\" tee continues to be one of our all-time best sellers. Little did I know when I designed this tee 9 years ago that it would become so popular<\/p>","enable_overlay":true,"enable_popup":false,"product_1":"amperstand-hat","product_2":"premium-black-aluminum-ampersand"}},"3a57d24b-4006-42f0-bb46-be79e14b82c9":{"type":"image","disabled":true,"settings":{"link":"","title":"","text":"<p>Gearing up for our big sale. Excited to release a bunch of new products too! Ge